title: Scott Eastwood dating Charlotte McKinney?
text:
Scott Eastwood has fuelled dating rumours with Charlotte McKinney after the couple were spotted enjoyed a date paddleboarding in Malibu earlier this week.
READ: Scott Eastwood to star in 'Overdrive'
The Longest Ride star was spotted paddleboarding with the 22-year-old model-and-actress in Malibu earlier this week, and couldn't keep their hands off one another, reported E!Online.
"They were all over each other--holding hands and getting touchy-feely. They were really cute and would make a gorgeous couple," a source said.
Despite their closeness, the alleged romance between the pair - who first met at the Teen Choice Awards - is new and not yet serious.
Eastwood, 29, previously admitted he would give up his career for love.
